    "FP represents the image that the model predicts to be strawberry anthracnose, but the true label is not strawberry anthracnose, i.e., the number of samples that are incorrectly predicted as positive.",
    "It indicates the proportion of samples that are actually positive in a sample that is predicted to be positive.",
    "The calculation process is shown in Equation 19.",
    "It measures the ability of the trained model to detect all classes.",
    "mAP/mAP 50 /mAP 75 is mAP IoU=0.5:0.05:0.95 /mAP IoU=0.5 /mAP IoU=0.75."
